{"tid":1322008,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【戒嚴】【香港人末日】香港人全部唔准去旅行","createTime":"2019-07-15T23:21:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T00:36:33.000Z","uid":54337,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b8f692a743e74c35f5c7e4d57b4afbb16f9765f7","tid":1322008,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T23:21:07.000Z","msg":"請參考台灣老蔣戒嚴令：<br />\n<br />\n依據《戒嚴法》規定：「在宣布戒嚴期間，由戒嚴地域的最高司令官掌管行政事務及司法事務」，政府為便利戰時管理而在國共內戰期間執行，人民自由與基本人權，包括集會、結社、言論、出版、<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">旅遊</span></span></strong>等權利被限縮，即所謂黨禁、報禁、海禁、<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">出口旅遊禁</span></span></strong>等，在此段時期言論自由受到普遍限制。"},{"pid":"f67937903ce5b5619f4ed054da1dcdaae4aff39c","tid":1322008,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T23:21:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E8%87%BA%E7%81%A3%E7%9C%81%E6%88%92%E5%9A%B4%E4%BB%A4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-tw%2F%25E8%2587%25BA%25E7%2581%25A3%25E7%259C%2581%25E6%2588%2592%25E5%259A%25B4%25E4%25BB%25A4&d=SZ2g%2FZg1uDubc4iNJejiXhmaKe8vvTAxx9uYoYxOzRs%3D&h=7a9e43d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E8%87%BA%E7%81%A3%E7%9C%81%E6%88%92%E5%9A%B4%E4%BB%A4</a>"},{"pid":"b2becc3bf0e762b1ed31e1e0d50e0326651806de","tid":1322008,"uid":54337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T23:21:57.000Z","msg":"同日本櫻花同溫泉講bye bye<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1b4f4d7f2f4428e6bebf90709f53bff0e549bec","tid":1322008,"uid":54337,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T23:27:32.000Z","msg":"稱霸全球，香港人每年可以遊埠幾多次？<br />\n<br />\n「死都要去旅行」或是每個香港人心中僅餘的一團火。隨著廉航增加，自由行風氣普及，無論周末速遊星馬泰，還是即日往返東京大阪，都成為了家常便飯，其威力甚至震驚了外國媒體。英國旅遊網站 MoveHub 最近調查了 111 個國家或地區的旅客數據，不包括出國讀書和商務用途，只計遊埠性質，每年人均離境旅遊次數最多的，放眼全球毫無對手，就是香港。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cup.com.hk/2017/09/28/worlds-biggest-traveller/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2F2017%2F09%2F28%2Fworlds-biggest-traveller%2F&d=SZ2g%2FZg1uDubc4iNJejiXhmaKe8vvTAxx9uYoYxOzRs%3D&h=71c61cfd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cup.com.hk/2017/09/28/worlds-biggest-traveller/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人去旅行去到成為世界第一嘅日子，應該完了。<br />\n<br />\n因為淋病如果宣傳戒嚴，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全部香港人都無得去旅行</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"eceacce98950731338dff10471745462c61bcc23","tid":1322008,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T23:32:04.000Z","msg":"香港一定跟台灣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8017059fb05c694b15a4ac3a2d44b1405e1d700f","tid":1322008,"uid":54337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T23:36:50.000Z","msg":"政治冷感的你，可以不問世事。<br />\n但如果你無得去旅行呢？<br />\n<br />\n台灣戒嚴38年。<br />\n如果你覺得可以38年都唔去旅行嘅話，<br />\n咁ok，你可以繼續不問世事"},{"pid":"03792f19a053f937323c882bf3d9dd926bd4d3bb","tid":1322008,"uid":54337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T23:38:28.000Z","msg":"撐警察的你，你可以繼續撐警察。<br />\n<br />\n台灣戒嚴38年。<br />\n如果你覺得可以38年都唔去旅行的話，<br />\n咁ok，咁你繼續撐香港警察。"},{"pid":"6b7bdd28d9e69d74f1ef1d86dc611b8df00b4929","tid":1322008,"uid":171192,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T23:40:03.000Z","msg":"經過今次件事我係外資都怕咗你香港<br />\n自己唔聽民意搞到一鑊泡要鎮壓遊行<br />\n依家又想戒嚴又想cut網絡<br />\n以為自己投資緊北韓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n國際金融中心定先軍政治中心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n亞太所有地方都係贏家<br />\n除咗香港<br />\n連北韓政府都同特朗普傾開放香港政府唔知喺度做緊乜春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81c111727c3785926ecffca912083060b85e34fe","tid":1322008,"uid":54337,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T23:52:55.000Z","msg":"根據香港政府2018年5月便覽：<br />\n<br />\n「旅遊業是香港的主要經濟支柱之一。2016年，旅遊業佔本地生產總值約5%，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就業人數約258 900人，佔全港總就業人數約7%。</span></span></strong>」<br />\n<br />\n一旦宣傳戒嚴，香港人無得出去外國旅行。<br />\n同樣道理，外國人亦無得來香港旅行。<br />\n<br />\n一旦戒嚴，258900旅遊從業員可以全部失業揸兜。<br />\n<br />\n從事旅遊業嘅你，你可以繼續撐政府，可以撐警察，可以繼續睇cctvb，屌班暴徒搞事。<br />\n<br />\n如果戒嚴，你覺得失業都無所謂嘅話，咁ok，<br />\n請你繼續撐政府，繼續撐警察。"},{"pid":"9f40d7180ca6301b1e9ebfb0a0240be1912b8251","tid":1322008,"uid":97240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T23:59:50.000Z","msg":"用外國passport 咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c934277630a1807a91606d00fdf6e2d278b20a7","tid":1322008,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f40d7180ca6301b1e9ebfb0a0240be1912b8251","tid":1322008,"uid":97240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T23:59:50.000Z","msg":"用外國passport 咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T00:04:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[入一入黎] 逃犯條例都壽終正寢啦點解仲要繼續撤？繼續撤回打爭者既控罪、追究警隊濫權、立即實行雙普選、反dq？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1321529\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1321529</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"44676fb6df5b709f6363d6684e80af0d114631b9","tid":1322008,"uid":75072,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T00:12:02.000Z","msg":"啱架啦 ！ 唔旅遊 唔返工，專心搞鳩你共產黨！"},{"pid":"d3cd2f3faccb746e45f2ab2dd94ebe5ad624d75d","tid":1322008,"uid":41477,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T00:17:05.000Z","msg":"包唔包括外國公民？"},{"pid":"70c6e84b2f7daf2bc705d5534244c2e6fc2db973","tid":1322008,"uid":97240,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d3c